{"tid":445104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭比梁振英更涼薄","createTime":"2017-10-23T05:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T05:42:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":727,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"5af244adc6dc143dbbe6bf0e9440204e8df93f04","tid":445104,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"禮賓府舉行勳銜頒授典禮，林鄭月娥追授金英勇勳章予殉職的消防總隊目邱少明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，邱氏遺孀偕同稚子上台代領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。這勳章是用性命換來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，沒什麼值得高興，只宜用肅穆的態度對待。因此，邱太神色凝重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，孩子一臉木然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20171023/large/e8809a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20171023%2Flarge%2Fe8809a.jpg&h=704f174b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是，頒授勳章的林鄭月娥不但笑，還要是最開懷的露齒笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16633979/art/20171023/20191101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16633979%2Fart%2F20171023%2F20191101&d=1lmE1RvqZIO5N38ZfiZK010Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=741a4125\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F16633979%2Fart%2F20171023%2F20191101&h=04b695bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/16633979/art/20171023/20191101</a></div>"},{"pid":"132a7da9ce9b4a8ab67b19aa08caa87fa2c9de95","tid":445104,"uid":1886,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"行政長官的歡欣，孤兒寡婦的哀傷，形成強烈對比，有相片捕捉到這詭異的瞬間，被張貼到藍絲聚集的「港人講地」，藍絲繼上次口誅筆伐屈穎妍後，再次展示港人該有的常識，以及說真話的勇氣，紛紛留言：「林鄭笑咩？」我腦海則浮現一張網絡圖片，韓義生指罵777，對白是：「笑甚麼，畜生，你也有老公的！」因殉職而獲勳，若你認為可喜可賀，是白痴；若你明知不幸，還肆無忌憚的笑，是涼薄。<br />\n<br />\n若你明知不幸，還肆無忌憚的笑，是涼薄。有網友找來從前梁振英追授勳章時的照片比較，發現連梁振英也懂得收起笑容，不敢像林太那樣咧嘴而笑。可見官到無求，不但大膽，還可能冷血。"},{"pid":"cc666b10f85fc7fe143554cd712c7cc4383c8b2b","tid":445104,"uid":1886,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"恭賀蔡若蓮喪子，至少有前因後果──即香港高官涼薄在先，於是有人憤而遷怒──但林鄭「超越人類道德底線」的一笑，又有什麼理由？難道以為頒獎時，笑是基本禮儀？假如林鄭開殯儀館，她一定很有禮貌地跟來客說：「歡迎光臨！」其實即使「笑喪」，正常人也不會在喪禮上笑，何況邱少明是英年早逝。<br />\n<br />\n對，這不是喪禮，但頒發勳章一刻，勢必勾起遺孀喪偶之痛，稚子失怙之戚，任何有同理心的人，哪怕瞎子，也會感同身受，歛卻笑容。邱氏妻兒的愁雲慘霧，隔着照片也撲面而來，林鄭不是盲的，面對面望着他們，還能笑逐顏開，有人性嗎？<br />\n<br />\n當然，林太可能面部肌肉抽筋，但無論是生理或心理問題，也請勿放棄治療。不要以為這是小事，無同理心的特首，制訂的政策又怎可能以民為本？做特首，最重要不是有國家底氣，而是有道德底線。喜歡譴責涼薄的校長去了哪裏？"},{"pid":"ea12b4d2fd14a082c9f8b99c6608764b8cc8fe85","tid":445104,"uid":29093,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"林奠月娥成個奠字掛起面上"},{"pid":"407be69e5f7135abd4084051d7eabd8c3c39f2e1","tid":445104,"uid":29093,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:34:00.000Z","msg":"香港啲狗官個撚個都政治敏感度不足"},{"pid":"ab19b7b90b50f7e93881c8167e8de822330bfb26","tid":445104,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a8dc8c2e13fee1d5d034fe06fb470d198ba1a4","tid":445104,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641afce6038dbc5f6e3c713beb69cd968bf5519e","tid":445104,"uid":49392,"like":18,"dislik